title: War of the Roses: His Ex-Wife Friended Her on Facebook
description: Darren is dating someone new and she became friends with his ex-wife.  He thought it would be good for them to get along because he has a child with her but then one day he came home to his new girlfriend and ex-wife in a compromising position.  What the heck is going on??
